\noindent{\it Appendix -- }

For completeness, we present the analytical expressions of the $F$ functions in Eq.~\eqref{eq:1}. The details of the derivations can be found in \cite{matterwave}. For the CSL model it is:

text:
\begin{equation}
\begin{split}
&F_{\text{\tiny dCSL}}(k,q,t)= \exp\Bigg[-\lambda \frac{m^2}{m_0^2} t \\ 
&\times \Big(1-\frac{1}{t} \int_0^t d\tau e^{-\frac{k^2r_C^2 k_T^2 }{\hbar^2} 
-\frac{(-\frac{k\tau}{m}+q)^2}{4r_C^2 (1+k_T)^2}}
e^{\frac{i(-k\tau+m q) 2k_T u_x }{\hbar(1+k_T)}}  \Big) \Bigg],
\end{split}
\end{equation}
